all_files <- function(files, dataset){
  len <- length(files)
  dataset <- read.csv(files[1])
  for (i in 2:len){
    a <- read.csv(files[i])
    dataset <- rbind(dataset, a)
  }
write.csv(dataset, "~/Desktop/bioinf/R statistics/merged_files.csv")
}

all_files(files, dataset) #             ,
